#: data/net.nokyan.Resources.metainfo.xml.in.in:17
msgid ""
"Resources allows you to check the utilization of your system resources and "
"control your running processes and apps. It’s designed to be user-friendly "
"and feel right at home on a modern desktop by using GNOME’s libadwaita."
msgstr ""
"Resurslar dasturi sizga tizim resurslaridan foydalanishni tekshirish hamda "
"ishlayotgan jarayon va ilovalaringizni boshqarish imkonini beradi. U "
"GNOME’ning libadwaita dasturidan foydalangan holda qulay va zamonaviy ish "
"stolida oʻzingizni uydagidek his qilishingiz uchun moʻljallangan."

